"data\": {\"body\": \"<p><strong>KURZ KRESBY \\u2013 odborn\\u00e9 veden\\u00ed: Mgr. Gabriela Bernardov\\u00e1</strong></p>\\n\\n<p>Budova: Praskova 399/8</p>\\n\\n<p>Cena kurzu: 1000,- K\\u010d</p>\\n\\n<p>Kurzovn\\u00e9 se hrad\\u00ed hotov\\u011b p\\u0159i zah\\u00e1jen\\u00ed prvn\\u00ed lekce.</p>\\n\\n<p>I. TURNUS / p\\u00e1tek / 14:00 \\u2013 16:00 / 9. 11. - 16. 11. - 23. 11. - 30. 11. - 7. 12.</p>\\n\\n<p>Volba od\\u011bvu a obuvi dle vlastn\\u00edho uv\\u00e1\\u017een\\u00ed (kresba tu\\u017ekou).<br>\\nPoskytujeme podlo\\u017eku, lep\\u00edc\\u00ed p\\u00e1sky, pap\\u00edr a tu\\u017eky (neposkytujeme gumu ke gumov\\u00e1n\\u00ed tu\\u017eky a fixativ).</p>\\n\\n<p>\\u00a0</p>\\n\\n<p><strong>KURZ MODELOV\\u00c1N\\u00cd \\u2013 odborn\\u00e9 veden\\u00ed: Petr Marcal\\u00edk</strong></p>\\n\\n<p>Budova: Jansk\\u00e1 1849/30</p>\\n\\n<p>Zah\\u00e1jen\\u00ed prvn\\u00ed lekce prob\\u011bhne na hlavn\\u00ed budov\\u011b (Praskova 399/8), odkud lektor doprovod\\u00ed \\u00fa\\u010dastn\\u00edky do c\\u00edlov\\u00e9 budovy.</p>\\n\\n<p>Cena kurzu: 1200,- K\\u010d</p>\\n\\n<p>Kurzovn\\u00e9 se hrad\\u00ed hotov\\u011b p\\u0159i zah\\u00e1jen\\u00ed prvn\\u00ed lekce.</p>\\n\\n<p>I. TURNUS / \\u00fater\\u00fd / 15:00 \\u2013 17:00 / 6. 11. - 13. 11. - 20. 11. - 27. 11. - 4. 12.</p>\\n\\n<p>II. TURNUS / st\\u0159eda / 17:00 \\u2013 19:00 / 7. 11. - 14. 11. - 21. 11. - 28. 11. - 5. 12.</p>\\n\\n<p>III. TURNUS / pond\\u011bl\\u00ed / 17:00 \\u2013 19:00 / 5. 11. - 12. 11. - 19. 11. - 26. 11. - 3. 12.</p>\\n\\n<p>III. turnus je stanoven\\u00fd jako kapacitn\\u00ed rezerva.</p>\\n\\n<p>Doporu\\u010dujeme od\\u011bv a obuv odpov\\u00eddaj\\u00edc\\u00ed pr\\u00e1ci se socha\\u0159skou hl\\u00ednou.</p>\\n\\n<p>Poskytujeme materi\\u00e1l a modelovac\\u00ed pom\\u016fcky (je mo\\u017en\\u00e9 pracovat s vlastn\\u00edmi pom\\u016fckami).</p>\\n\\n<p>\\u00a0</p>\\n\\n<hr>\\n<p>\\u00a0</p>\\n\\n<p><strong>P\\u0159ihl\\u00e1\\u0161en\\u00ed: osobn\\u011b na T\\u00fddnu otev\\u0159en\\u00fdch dve\\u0159\\u00ed nebo na emailu <a href=\\\"mailto:anlauf@sspu-opava.cz\\\">anlauf@sspu-opava.cz</a><br>\\nInformace: 733 674 693 nebo anlauf@sspu-opava.cz</strong></p>\"}, \"parent_id\": null, \"position\": 0, \"plugin_type\": \"TextPlugin\"}], \"order\": [3033], \"parent_id\": null}','cs',1,542,244),(552,'add_plugin','{\"order\": [3034], \"parent_id\": null}','{\"plugins\": [{\"pk\": 3034, \"creation_date\": \"2018-10-12T06:32:47.561Z\", \"data\": {\"body\": \"<p>Jak jste ji\\u017e \\u010detli na na\\u0161ich str\\u00e1nk\\u00e1ch, dru\\u017estvo atlet\\u016f v z\\u00e1\\u0159\\u00ed vybojovalo 3. m\\u00edsto v okrese. V posledn\\u00edm z\\u00e1\\u0159ijov\\u00e9m v\\u00edkendu jsme se dozv\\u011bd\\u011bli, \\u017ee v\\u00edt\\u011bzov\\u00e9 okresu ze \\\"Zem\\u011bd\\u011blky\\\" se krajsk\\u00e9ho fin\\u00e1le nez\\u00fa\\u010dastn\\u00ed, tak\\u017ee na\\u0161e dru\\u017estvo postupuje m\\u00edsto nich. Chv\\u00e1la bohu za internet a \\u0160kolu online; d\\u00edky tomu se n\\u00e1m poda\\u0159ilo svolat dru\\u017estvo a roz\\u0161\\u00ed\\u0159it ho o dal\\u0161\\u00ed \\u010dleny.</p>\\n\\n<div>V \\u00fater\\u00fd 2. \\u0159\\u00edjna 2018 si na n\\u00e1s po\\u010das\\u00ed v Opav\\u011b p\\u0159ichystalo nejhor\\u0161\\u00ed den cel\\u00e9ho t\\u00fddne. P\\u0159i n\\u00e1stupu dru\\u017estev mrholilo a byla zima. Na\\u0161t\\u011bst\\u00ed se postupn\\u011b mraky roztrhaly, slun\\u00ed\\u010dko p\\u0159ece jen zasv\\u00edtilo a hnalo atlety ke skv\\u011bl\\u00fdm v\\u00fdkon\\u016fm.</div>\\n\\n<div>Na\\u0161i borci za to vzali hned od za\\u010d\\u00e1tku. Daniel Holuscha byl druh\\u00fd na 60 m. Tak\\u00e9 ve vrhu koul\\u00ed, na\\u0161\\u00ed slabin\\u011b v okresu, do\\u0161lo k v\\u00fdrazn\\u00e9mu zlep\\u0161en\\u00ed. David Dumbrovsk\\u00fd sv\\u00fdm v\\u00fdkonem obsadil 4. m\\u00edsto a Mirek Zeisberger mu zdatn\\u011b sekundoval. Luk\\u00e1\\u0161 V\\u00edcha se ji\\u017e dal zdravotn\\u011b do po\\u0159\\u00e1dku, co\\u017e potvrdil 4. m\\u00edstem na 400 m a 5. m\\u00edstem na 1500 m. Asi nejv\\u00edce, jsme tentokr\\u00e1t, ztratili na v\\u00fd\\u0161ce, kde v\\u00edt\\u011bz sko\\u010dil 198 cm. P\\u0159esto si Sebastian \\u0160van\\u010dar polep\\u0161il na 166 cm a obsadil 7. m\\u00edsto. Andreas Pisko\\u0159 pak sv\\u00fdm 5. m\\u00edstem v d\\u00e1lce p\\u0159ihodil tak\\u00e9 slu\\u0161n\\u00fd po\\u010det bod\\u016f. \\u0160tafeta na 4 x 200 m ve slo\\u017een\\u00ed Holuscha, Pisko\\u0159, V\\u00edcha, \\u0160van\\u010dar pak v\\u0161e korunovala skv\\u011bl\\u00fdm 1. m\\u00edstem. V kone\\u010dn\\u00e9m sou\\u010dtu bod\\u016f jsme obsadili \\u00fa\\u017easn\\u00e9 3. m\\u00edsto a pouze 10 bod\\u016f n\\u00e1s d\\u011blilo od druh\\u00e9ho m\\u00edsta. Holt sm\\u016fla, ale co se d\\u00e1 d\\u011blat.</div>\\n\\n<div>V\\u0161em reprezentant\\u016fm pat\\u0159\\u00ed velk\\u00fd d\\u00edk za odhodl\\u00e1n\\u00ed a v\\u00fdkony, kter\\u00e9 za nep\\u0159\\u00edzn\\u011b po\\u010das\\u00ed p\\u0159edv\\u00e1d\\u011bli.</div>\\n\\n<div>Slo\\u017een\\u00ed dru\\u017estva: <strong>Martin Bl\\u00e1ha, David Dumbrovsk\\u00fd, Martin Dzida, Daniel Holuscha, Andreas Pisko\\u0159, Sebastian \\u0160van\\u010dar, Jan Vavre\\u010dka, Luk\\u00e1\\u0161 V\\u00edcha, David Engli\\u0161, Miroslav Zeisberger</strong>.</div>\\n\\n<div>\\u00a0</div>\\n\\n<div>\\u00a0</div>\\n\\n<div><em>Mgr. Zuzana Holu\\u0161ov\\u00e1</em></div>\"}, \"parent_id\": null, \"position\": 0, \"plugin_type\": \"TextPlugin\"}], \"order\": [3034], \"parent_id\": null}','cs',1,543,245),(553,'add_plugin','{\"order\": [3035], \"parent_id\": null}','{\"plugins\": [{\"pk\": 3035, \"creation_date\": \"2018-10-12T06:38:21.610Z\", \"data\": {\"body\": \"<p>Dnes to v t\\u011blocvi\\u010dn\\u011b pra\\u0161t\\u011blo tv\\u016fr\\u010d\\u00edmi v\\u00fdboji. Ovl\\u00e1dla ji v\\u00edce ne\\u017e stovka \\u017e\\u00e1k\\u016f z\\u00e1kladn\\u00edch \\u0161kol. Mezi n\\u011b se vm\\u00edsila bizarn\\u00ed sm\\u011bsice kost\\u00fdmovan\\u00fdch model\\u016f (na\\u0161ich \\u010dtvr\\u0165\\u00e1k\\u016f-um\\u011blc\\u016f) a objekt\\u016f (pr\\u00e1ce na\\u0161ich um\\u011blc\\u016f). Nabitou atmosf\\u00e9ru usm\\u011br\\u0148ovaly kolegyn\\u011b Mgr. Lenka Ka\\u0161p\\u00e1rkov\\u00e1, Ph.D. a MgA. Lenka Szwedov\\u00e1 pod veden\\u00edm Mgr. Daniely Kubov\\u00e9.</p>\\n\\n<div>\\u00a0</div>\\n\\n<div>Touto d\\u017eungl\\u00ed se mistrn\\u011b propl\\u00e9tal mr\\u0161tn\\u00fd fotograf MgA. Ji\\u0159\\u00ed \\u0160tencek, z jeho\\u017e expozic vyb\\u00edr\\u00e1me n\\u011bkolik kousk\\u016f.</div>\\n\\n<div>\\u00a0</div>\\n\\n<div>V z\\u00e1v\\u011bru sout\\u011b\\u017ee se jmenovan\\u00ed prom\\u011bnili v porotce a v ka\\u017ed\\u00e9 ze t\\u0159\\u00ed v\\u011bkov\\u00fdch kategori\\u00ed vybrali nejlep\\u0161\\u00ed pr\\u00e1ce k ocen\\u011bn\\u00ed.</div>\\n\\n<div>\\u00a0</div>\\n\\n<div><strong>Vybran\\u00e1 d\\u00edlka budou vystaven\\u00e1 10. - 12. 10. od 8:00 do 17:00 v p\\u0159\\u00edzem\\u00ed \\u0161koly v prav\\u00e9m k\\u0159\\u00eddle v r\\u00e1mci T\\u00fddne otev\\u0159en\\u00fdch dve\\u0159\\u00ed. Vernis\\u00e1\\u017e a p\\u0159ed\\u00e1n\\u00ed cen prob\\u011bhne v 9. 10. v 15:00.</strong></div>\\n\\n<p>D\\u011bkujeme v\\u0161em z\\u00fa\\u010dastn\\u011bn\\u00fdm i organiz\\u00e1tor\\u016fm!</p>\\n\\n<div>\\n<hr></div>\\n\\n<div>A zde je listina v\\u00fdherc\\u016f:</div>\\n\\n<p>\\u00a0</p>\\n\\n<div><strong>I. kategorie (6 - 8 let)</strong></div>\\n\\n<p>1. m\\u00edsto - Viktorie Malch\\u00e1rkov\\u00e1 / Z\\u0160 Bolatice<br>\\n2. m\\u00edsto -\\u00a0 Linda Majewsk\\u00e1 / Z\\u0160 Ma\\u0159\\u00e1dkova<br>\\n3. m\\u00edsto - Karol\\u00edna Ond\\u0159ejov\\u00e1 / Z\\u0160 Ma\\u0159\\u00e1dkova<br>\\n\\u010destn\\u00e9 uzn\\u00e1n\\u00ed - Zuzana Jochimov\\u00e1 / Z\\u0160 Bolatice</p>\\n\\n<div>\\u00a0</div>\\n\\n<div><strong>II. kategorie (9 - 12 let)</strong></div>\\n\\n<p>1. m\\u00edsto - Am\\u00e1lie Podrazk\\u00e1 / Z\\u0160 Bo\\u017eeny N\\u011bmcov\\u00e9<br>\\n2. m\\u00edsto - Simona Zl\\u00e1malov\\u00e1 / Z\\u0160 Budi\\u0161ov n.B.<br>\\n3. m\\u00edsto - Sofia Pendzichov\\u00e1 / Z\\u0160 \\u0160r\\u00e1mkova<br>\\n\\u010destn\\u00e9 uzn\\u00e1n\\u00ed - Julie Hejdukov\\u00e1 / Z\\u0160 Bo\\u017eeny N\\u011bmcov\\u00e9</p>\\n\\n<div>\\u00a0</div>\\n\\n<div><strong>III. kategorie (13 - 15 let)</strong></div>\\n\\n<p>1. m\\u00edsto - Veronika Ja\\u0161kov\\u00e1 / Z\\u0160 Engli\\u0161ova<br>\\n2. m\\u00edsto - Hana Jirk\\u016f / Z\\u0160 Bo\\u017eeny N\\u011bmcov\\u00e9<br>\\n3. m\\u00edsto - Kl\\u00e1ra Godulov\\u00e1 / Z\\u0160 Engli\\u0161ova<br>\\n\\u010destn\\u00e9 uzn\\u00e1n\\u00ed - Filip Gu\\u017eiak / Z\\u0160 Engli\\u0161ova</p>\\n\\n<div><em>V\\u00fdherc\\u016fm gratulujeme!</em></div>\"}, \"parent_id\": null, \"position\": 0, \"plugin_type\": \"TextPlugin\"}], \"order\": [3035], \"parent_id\": null}','cs',1,544,246),(554,'add_plugin','{\"order\": [3035], \"parent_id\": null}','{\"plugins\": [{\"pk\": 3036, \"creation_date\": \"2018-10-12T06:44:12.717Z\", \"data\": {\"theme\": \"default\", \"options\": \"\"}, \"parent_id\": null, \"position\": 1, \"plugin_type\": \"GalleryPlugin\"}], \"order\": [3035, 3036], \"parent_id\": null}','cs',1,545,246),(555,'add_plugin','{\"order\": [3037], \"parent_id\": null}','{\"plugins\": [{\"pk\": 3037, \"creation_date\": \"2018-10-12T06:49:24.364Z\", \"data\": {\"body\": \"<div>V t\\u00fddnu od 16. 9. do 21. 9. 2018 absolvovali studenti t\\u0159\\u00eddy U3 kurz malby a kresby v plen\\u00e9ru pod veden\\u00edm u\\u010ditel\\u016f um\\u011bleck\\u00fdch obor\\u016f Lenky Ka\\u0161p\\u00e1rkov\\u00e9, Lenky Szwedov\\u00e9 a s dozorem t\\u0159\\u00eddn\\u00ed u\\u010ditelky Pavly Nedopilkov\\u00e9. P\\u0159esto\\u017ee je to kurz povinn\\u00fd, studenti se na n\\u011bj ka\\u017edoro\\u010dn\\u011b velmi t\\u011b\\u0161\\u00ed. Maj\\u00ed si zde toti\\u017e mo\\u017enost vyzkou\\u0161et i v\\u00fdtvarn\\u00e9 techniky a p\\u0159\\u00edstupy, se kter\\u00fdmi se v b\\u011b\\u017en\\u00e9 v\\u00fduce nesetk\\u00e1vaj\\u00ed, a v neposledn\\u00ed \\u0159ad\\u011b je tento p\\u011btidenn\\u00ed kurs skv\\u011blou p\\u0159\\u00edle\\u017eitost\\u00ed k utu\\u017een\\u00ed kolektivu t\\u0159\\u00eddy i k nav\\u00e1z\\u00e1n\\u00ed hlub\\u0161\\u00edho kontaktu pedagog\\u016f s \\u017e\\u00e1ky.</div>\\n\\n<div>Tentokr\\u00e1t jsme se se studenty vypravili do malebn\\u00e9 p\\u0159\\u00edrody Jesen\\u00edk\\u016f, do Doln\\u00ed Moravice, kde vzniklo velk\\u00e9 mno\\u017estv\\u00ed velmi kvalitn\\u00edch prac\\u00ed inspirovan\\u00fdch n\\u00e1dhernou p\\u0159\\u00edrodou. P\\u0159\\u00ednosem malov\\u00e1n\\u00ed v plen\\u00e9ru je bezesporu tak\\u00e9 to, \\u017ee se zde v\\u011bt\\u0161ina student\\u016f kresebn\\u011b uvoln\\u00ed, co\\u017e se potom z\\u00e1konit\\u011b projev\\u00ed i lep\\u0161\\u00edmi v\\u00fdsledky \\u0161koln\\u00edch prac\\u00ed v praktick\\u00fdch p\\u0159edm\\u011btech. \\u00da\\u010dastn\\u00edci leto\\u0161n\\u00edho plen\\u00e9ru p\\u0159istupovali ke sv\\u00e9 pr\\u00e1ci velmi kreativn\\u011b, vyzkou\\u0161eli si nejen klasick\\u00e9 kresebn\\u00e9 techniky, jako nap\\u0159\\u00edklad kresbu uhlem, tu\\u017ekou, perem \\u010di rudkou, ale pou\\u0161t\\u011bli se tak\\u00e9 do r\\u016fzn\\u00fdch mal\\u00ed\\u0159sk\\u00fdch a kombinovan\\u00fdch technik.</div>\\n\\n<div>Pr\\u00e1ce byla v ka\\u017ed\\u00e9m dni rozd\\u011blena do dvou blok\\u016f, kdy studenti dostali zadan\\u00fd \\u00fakol \\u010di t\\u00e9ma, nap\\u0159. krajina, zv\\u00ed\\u0159ata, architektura, apod. Ka\\u017ed\\u00fd ve\\u010der byla pr\\u00e1ce student\\u016fm \\u00fastn\\u011b hodnocena a okomentov\\u00e1na.</div>\\n\\n<p>V r\\u00e1mci plen\\u00e9ru byli tak\\u00e9 studenti ka\\u017ed\\u00e9 dopoledne od 8 \\u2013 10 hodin \\u00fastn\\u011b zkou\\u0161eni z anglick\\u00e9ho jazyka jako p\\u0159\\u00edprava k maturitn\\u00ed zkou\\u0161ce.<br>\\nVybran\\u00e9 pr\\u00e1ce jsou vystaveny na chodb\\u011b v 1. pat\\u0159e a ve\\u0159ejnosti budou p\\u0159\\u00edstupn\\u00e9 b\\u011bhem<strong> T\\u00fddnu otev\\u0159en\\u00fdch dve\\u0159\\u00ed 8. - 12. 10. od 8:00 do 17:00 hodin</strong>.</p>\\n\\n<div><em>Mgr. Pavla Nadopilkov\\u00e1, t\\u0159\\u00eddn\\u00ed u\\u010ditelka</em></div>\"}, \"parent_id\": null, \"position\": 0, \"plugin_type\": \"TextPlugin\"}], \"order\": [3037], \"parent_id\": null}','cs',1,546,247),(556,'add_plugin','{\"order\": [3037], \"parent_id\": null}','{\"plugins\": [{\"pk\": 3038, \"creation_date\": \"2018-10-12T06:52:23.375Z\", \"data\": {\"theme\": \"default\", \"options\": \"\"}, \"parent_id\": null, \"position\": 1, \"plugin_type\": \"GalleryPlugin\"}], \"order\": [3037, 3038], \"parent_id\": null}','cs',1,547,247),(557,'change_plugin','{\"plugins\": [{\"pk\": 3037, \"creation_date\": \"2018-10-12T06:49:24.364Z\", \"data\": {\"body\": \"<div>V t\\u00fddnu od 16. 9. do 21. 9. 2018 absolvovali studenti t\\u0159\\u00eddy U3 kurz malby a kresby v plen\\u00e9ru pod veden\\u00edm u\\u010ditel\\u016f um\\u011bleck\\u00fdch obor\\u016f Lenky Ka\\u0161p\\u00e1rkov\\u00e9, Lenky Szwedov\\u00e9 a s dozorem t\\u0159\\u00eddn\\u00ed u\\u010ditelky Pavly Nedopilkov\\u00e9. P\\u0159esto\\u017ee je to kurz povinn\\u00fd, studenti se na n\\u011bj ka\\u017edoro\\u010dn\\u011b velmi t\\u011b\\u0161\\u00ed. Maj\\u00ed si zde toti\\u017e mo\\u017enost vyzkou\\u0161et i v\\u00fdtvarn\\u00e9 techniky a p\\u0159\\u00edstupy, se kter\\u00fdmi se v b\\u011b\\u017en\\u00e9 v\\u00fduce nesetk\\u00e1vaj\\u00ed, a v neposledn\\u00ed \\u0159ad\\u011b je tento p\\u011btidenn\\u00ed kurs skv\\u011blou p\\u0159\\u00edle\\u017eitost\\u00ed k utu\\u017een\\u00ed kolektivu t\\u0159\\u00eddy i k nav\\u00e1z\\u00e1n\\u00ed hlub\\u0161\\u00edho kontaktu pedagog\\u016f s \\u017e\\u00e1ky.</div>\\n\\n<div>Tentokr\\u00e1t jsme se se studenty vypravili do malebn\\u00e9 p\\u0159\\u00edrody Jesen\\u00edk\\u016f, do Doln\\u00ed Moravice, kde vzniklo velk\\u00e9 mno\\u017estv\\u00ed velmi kvalitn\\u00edch