18-10-12T06:32:47.561Z\", \"data\": {\"body\": \"<p>Jak jste ji\\u017e \\u010detli na na\\u0161ich str\\u00e1nk\\u00e1ch, dru\\u017estvo atlet\\u016f v z\\u00e1\\u0159\\u00ed vybojovalo 3. m\\u00edsto v okrese. V posledn\\u00edm z\\u00e1\\u0159ijov\\u00e9m v\\u00edkendu jsme se dozv\\u011bd\\u011bli, \\u017ee v\\u00edt\\u011bzov\\u00e9 okresu ze \\\"Zem\\u011bd\\u011blky\\\" se krajsk\\u00e9ho fin\\u00e1le nez\\u00fa\\u010dastn\\u00ed, tak\\u017ee na\\u0161e dru\\u017estvo postupuje m\\u00edsto nich. Chv\\u00e1la bohu za internet a \\u0160kolu online; d\\u00edky tomu se n\\u00e1m poda\\u0159ilo svolat dru\\u017estvo a roz\\u0161\\u00ed\\u0159it ho o dal\\u0161\\u00ed \\u010dleny.</p>\\n\\n<div>V \\u00fater\\u00fd 2. \\u0159\\u00edjna 2018 si na n\\u00e1s po\\u010das\\u00ed v Opav\\u011b p\\u0159ichystalo nejhor\\u0161\\u00ed den cel\\u00e9ho t\\u00fddne. P\\u0159i n\\u00e1stupu dru\\u017estev mrholilo a byla zima. Na\\u0161t\\u011bst\\u00ed se postupn\\u011b mraky roztrhaly, slun\\u00ed\\u010dko p\\u0159ece jen zasv\\u00edtilo a hnalo atlety ke skv\\u011bl\\u00fdm v\\u00fdkon\\u016fm.</div>\\n\\n<div>Na\\u0161i borci za to vzali hned od za\\u010d\\u00e1tku. Daniel Holuscha byl druh\\u00fd na 60 m. Tak\\u00e9 ve vrhu koul\\u00ed, na\\u0161\\u00ed slabin\\u011b v okresu, do\\u0161lo k v\\u00fdrazn\\u00e9mu zlep\\u0161en\\u00ed. David Dumbrovsk\\u00fd sv\\u00fdm v\\u00fdkonem obsadil 4. m\\u00edsto a Mirek Zeisberger mu zdatn\\u011b sekundoval. Luk\\u00e1\\u0161 V\\u00edcha se ji\\u017e dal zdravotn\\u011b do po\\u0159\\u00e1dku, co\\u017e potvrdil 4. m\\u00edstem na 400 m a 5. m\\u00edstem na 1500 m. Asi nejv\\u00edce, jsme tentokr\\u00e1t, ztratili na v\\u00fd\\u0161ce, kde v\\u00edt\\u011bz sko\\u010dil 198 cm. P\\u0159esto si Sebastian \\u0160van\\u010dar polep\\u0161il na 166 cm a obsadil 7. m\\u00edsto. Andreas Pisko\\u0159 pak sv\\u00fdm 5. m\\u00edstem v d\\u00e1lce p\\u0159ihodil tak\\u00e9 slu\\u0161n\\u00fd po\\u010det bod\\u016f. \\u0160tafeta na 4 x 200 m ve slo\\u017een\\u00ed Holuscha, Pisko\\u0159, V\\u00edcha, \\u0160van\\u010dar pak v\\u0161e korunovala skv\\u011bl\\u00fdm 1. m\\u00edstem. V kone\\u010dn\\u00e9m sou\\u010dtu bod\\u016f jsme obsadili \\u00fa\\u017easn\\u00e9 3. m\\u00edsto a pouze 10 bod\\u016f n\\u00e1s d\\u011blilo od druh\\u00e9ho m\\u00edsta. Holt sm\\u016fla, ale co se d\\u00e1 d\\u011blat.</div>\\n\\n<div>V\\u0161em reprezentant\\u016fm pat\\u0159\\u00ed velk\\u00fd d\\u00edk za odhodl\\u00e1n\\u00ed a v\\u00fdkony, kter\\u00e9 za nep\\u0159\\u00edzn\\u011b po\\u010das\\u00ed p\\u0159edv\\u00e1d\\u011bli.</div>\\n\\n<div>Slo\\u017een\\u00ed dru\\u017estva: <strong>Martin Bl\\u00e1ha, David Dumbrovsk\\u00fd, Martin Dzida, Daniel Holuscha, Andreas Pisko\\u0159, Sebastian \\u0160van\\u010dar, Jan Vavre\\u010dka, Luk\\u00e1\\u0161 V\\u00edcha, David Engli\\u0161, Miroslav Zeisberger</strong>.</div>\\n\\n<div>\\u00a0</div>\\n\\n<div>\\u00a0</div>\\n\\n<div><em>Mgr. Zuzana Holu\\u0161ov\\u00e1</em></div>\"}, \"parent_id\": null, \"position\": 0, \"plugin_type\": \"TextPlugin\"}]}','{\"plugins\": [{\"pk\": 3034, \"creation_date\": \"2018-10-12T06:32:47.561Z\", \"data\": {\"body\": \"<div>V \\u00fater\\u00fd 2. \\u0159\\u00edjna 2018 si na n\\u00e1s po\\u010das\\u00ed v Opav\\u011b p\\u0159ichystalo nejhor\\u0161\\u00ed den cel\\u00e9ho t\\u00fddne. P\\u0159i n\\u00e1stupu dru\\u017estev mrholilo a byla zima. Na\\u0161t\\u011bst\\u00ed se postupn\\u011b mraky roztrhaly, slun\\u00ed\\u010dko p\\u0159ece jen zasv\\u00edtilo a hnalo atlety ke skv\\u011bl\\u00fdm v\\u00fdkon\\u016fm.</div>\\n\\n<div>Na\\u0161i borci za to vzali hned od za\\u010d\\u00e1tku. Daniel Holuscha byl druh\\u00fd na 60 m. Tak\\u00e9 ve vrhu koul\\u00ed, na\\u0161\\u00ed slabin\\u011b v okresu, do\\u0161lo k v\\u00fdrazn\\u00e9mu zlep\\u0161en\\u00ed. David Dumbrovsk\\u00fd sv\\u00fdm v\\u00fdkonem obsadil 4. m\\u00edsto a Mirek Zeisberger mu zdatn\\u011b sekundoval. Luk\\u00e1\\u0161 V\\u00edcha se ji\\u017e dal zdravotn\\u011b