 1. m\\u00edsto \\u2013 60 m, 2. m\\u00edsto \\u2013 skok dalek\\u00fd</li>\\n\\t<li><strong>Andreas Pisko\\u0159</strong>: 1. m\\u00edsto \\u2013 skok dalek\\u00fd</li>\\n\\t<li><strong>Sebastian \\u0160van\\u010dar</strong>: 3. m\\u00edsto \\u2013 skok vysok\\u00fd</li>\\n\\t<li><strong>Luk\\u00e1\\u0161 V\\u00edcha</strong>: 2. m\\u00edsto \\u2013 1500 m</li>\\n</ul>\\n\\n<p>Celkov\\u011b jsme se um\\u00edstili na kr\\u00e1sn\\u00e9m 3. m\\u00edst\\u011b, pouh\\u00fdch 95 bod\\u016f n\\u00e1s d\\u011blilo od st\\u0159\\u00edbrn\\u00e9 medaile. Do p\\u0159\\u00ed\\u0161t\\u00edho roku je tak na\\u0161e dru\\u017estvo p\\u0159\\u00edslibem, proto\\u017ee jej tvo\\u0159ili pouze ho\\u0161i 1. a 2. ro\\u010dn\\u00edku. Pokud se tedy mezi na\\u0161imi studenty najde do dal\\u0161\\u00edho ro\\u010dn\\u00edku n\\u011bjak\\u00fd \\u0161ikovn\\u00fd koula\\u0159, p\\u0159\\u00edpadn\\u011b skokan do v\\u00fd\\u0161ky, m\\u016f\\u017eeme pom\\u00fd\\u0161let i na stupe\\u0148 nejvy\\u0161\\u0161\\u00ed.</p>\\n\\n<div>V\\u0161em atletick\\u00fdm reprezentant\\u016fm d\\u011bkuji za p\\u0159edveden\\u00e9 v\\u00fdkony a vzornou reprezentaci \\u0161koly.</div>\\n\\n<div>Slo\\u017een\\u00ed dru\\u017estva: <strong>SV1A: Luk\\u00e1\\u0161 V\\u00edcha, Martin Bl\\u00e1ha, Michal Sekanina, SV2A: Jan Vavre\\u010dka, Sebastian \\u0160van\\u010dar, SV2B: Daniel Holuscha, IT2: Andreas Pisko\\u0159, David Dumbrovsk\\u00fd, Martin Dzida.</strong></div>\\n\\n<div>\\u00a0</div>\\n\\n<div><em>Mgr. Zuzana Holu\\u0161ov\\u00e1</em></div>\"}, \"parent_id\": null, \"position\": 1, \"plugin_type\": \"TextPlugin\"}], \"order\": [3039, 3040], \"parent_id\": null}','cs',1,550,248),(560,'add_plugin','{\"order\": [3039, 3040], \"parent_id\": null}','{\"plugins\": [{\"pk\": 3041, \"creation_date\": \"2018-10-12T06:59:38.532Z\", \"data\": {\"theme\": \"default\", \"options\": \"\"}, \"parent_id\": null, \"position\": 2, \"plugin_type\": \"GalleryPlugin\"}], \"order\": [3039, 3040, 3041], \"parent_id