lass=\\\"popular-course-content\\\">\\n<h5>Adapta\\u010dn\\u00ed pobyt</h5>\\n\\n<p>S \\u00fasm\\u011bvem a v dobr\\u00e9m kolektivu jde v\\u0161echno l\\u00edp, co\\u017e plat\\u00ed i o studiu na st\\u0159edn\\u00ed \\u0161kole. A tak hned v prvn\\u00edch z\\u00e1\\u0159ijov\\u00fdch dnech se nov\\u011b utvo\\u0159en\\u00e9 t\\u0159\\u00eddy i se sv\\u00fdmi t\\u0159\\u00eddn\\u00edmi u\\u010diteli vz\\u00e1jemn\\u011b pozn\\u00e1vaj\\u00ed na adapta\\u010dn\\u00edm kurzu v malebn\\u00e9m prost\\u0159ed\\u00ed \\u0160tramberka i jeho kr\\u00e1sn\\u00e9ho okol\\u00ed.</p>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n\\n<div class=\\\"col-md-6 p-0\\\"><img class=\\\"img-responsive\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"img\\\\bg-img\\\\bg-2.jpg\\\"><cms-plugin title=\\\"Picture / Image - 4764\\\" alt=\\\"Picture / Image - 4764 \\\" id=\\\"4764\\\"></cms-plugin></div>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n\\n<div class=\\\"carousel-item\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"single-top-popular-course\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"row\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"col-md-6\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"popular-course-content\\\">\\n<h5>Odborn\\u00e1 v\\u00fduka</h5>\\n\\n<p>Podstatn\\u00e1 \\u010d\\u00e1st odborn\\u011b zam\\u011b\\u0159en\\u00e9 v\\u00fduky oboru informa\\u010dn\\u00ed technologie se odehr\\u00e1v\\u00e1 v budov\\u011b laborato\\u0159\\u00ed soused\\u00edc\\u00ed s hlavn\\u00ed budovou \\u0161koly. K sv\\u00e9mu studiu \\u017e\\u00e1ci krom\\u011b u\\u010deben vybaven\\u00fdch modern\\u00ed technikou vyu\\u017e\\u00edvaj\\u00ed i \\u0161koln\\u00ed e-learningov\\u00fd syst\\u00e9m Moodle.</p>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n\\n<div class=\\\"col-md-6 p-0\\\"><img class=\\\"img-responsive\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"img\\\\bg-img\\\\bg-2.jpg\\\"><cms-plugin title=\\\"Picture / Image - 4765\\\" alt=\\\"Picture / Image - 4765 \\\" id=\\\"4765\\\"></cms-plugin></div>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n\\n<div class=\\\"carousel-item\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"single-top-popular-course\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"row\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"col-md-6\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"popular-course-content\\\">\\n<h5>Ly\\u017ea\\u0159sk\\u00fd kurz</h5>\\n\\n<p>V prvn\\u00edm ro\\u010dn\\u00edku se mohou n\\u00e1ru\\u017eiv\\u00ed ly\\u017ea\\u0159i \\u010di snowbor\\u010f\\u00e1ci, ale i ti, kte\\u0159\\u00ed na zasn\\u011b\\u017een\\u00fdch svaz\\u00edch teprve za\\u010d\\u00ednaj\\u00ed, t\\u011b\\u0161it na t\\u00fddenn\\u00ed pobyt v Jesen\\u00edk\\u00e1ch. Chata Barborka a sjezdovky na Prad\\u011bdu jim k tomu poskytnou ide\\u00e1ln\\u00ed prost\\u0159ed\\u00ed.</p>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n\\n<div class=\\\"col-md-6\\\"><img class=\\\"img-responsive\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"img\\\\bg-img\\\\bg-2.jpg\\\"><cms-plugin title=\\\"Picture / Image - 4766\\\" alt=\\\"Picture / Image - 4766 \\\" id=\\\"4766\\\"></cms-plugin></div>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n\\n<div class=\\\"carousel-item\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"single-top-popular-course\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"row\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"col-md-6\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"popular-course-content\\\">\\n<h5>Samostatn\\u00e9 projekty</h5>\\n\\n<p>Podstatnou \\u010d\\u00e1st odborn\\u00e9 v\\u00fduky tvo\\u0159\\u00ed \\u0159e\\u0161en\\u00ed praktick\\u00fdch \\u00faloh a samostatn\\u00fdch projekt\\u016f. Vlastn\\u00ed webov\\u00e9 str\\u00e1nky, programov\\u00e9 aplikace, animovanou trojrozm\\u011brnou grafiku, n\\u00e1vrhy po\\u010d\\u00edta\\u010dov\\u00fdch s\\u00edt\\u00ed i hardwarov\\u00fdch za\\u0159\\u00edzen\\u00ed prezentuj\\u00ed jejich auto\\u0159i p\\u0159ed sv\\u00fdmi spolu\\u017e\\u00e1ky.</p>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n\\n<div class=\\\"col-md-6\\\"><img class=\\\"img-responsive\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"img\\\\bg-img\\\\bg-2.jpg\\\"><cms-plugin title=\\\"Picture / Image - 4767\\\" alt=\\\"Picture / Image - 4767 \\\" id=\\\"4767\\\"></cms-plugin></div>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n\\n<div class=\\\"carousel-item\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"single-top-popular-course\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"row\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"col-md-6\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"popular-course-content\\\">\\n<h5>Cykloturistick\\u00fd kurz</h5>\\n\\n<p>\\u010cervnov\\u00fd t\\u00fdden p\\u0159ev\\u00e1\\u017en\\u011b v sedlech bicykl\\u016f pro\\u017e\\u00edvaj\\u00ed \\u017e\\u00e1ci t\\u0159et\\u00edch ro\\u010dn\\u00edk\\u016f technick\\u00fdch obor\\u016f. V doprovodu sv\\u00fdch u\\u010ditel\\u016f projedou des\\u00edtky kilometr\\u016f po nejhez\\u010d\\u00edch cyklostezk\\u00e1ch v okol\\u00ed Opavy.</p>\\n\\n<p>Odkaz na \\u010dl\\u00e1nek</p>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n\\n<div class=\\\"col-md-6\\\"><img class=\\\"img-responsive\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"img\\\\bg-img\\\\bg-2.jpg\\\"><cms-plugin title=\\\"Picture / Image - 4768\\\" alt=\\\"Picture / Image - 4768 \\\" id=\\\"4768\\\"></cms-plugin></div>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n\\n<div class=\\\"carousel-item\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"single-top-popular-course\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"row\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"col-md-6\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"popular-course-content\\\">\\n<h5>Certifik\\u00e1ty z angli\\u010dtiny</h5>\\n\\n<p>Znalost ciz\\u00edch jazyk\\u016f je nezbytn\\u00e1 k z\\u00edsk\\u00e1n\\u00ed atraktivn\\u00edho zam\\u011bstn\\u00e1n\\u00ed i branou do sv\\u011bta. Ve spolupr\\u00e1ci s jazykovou \\u0161kolou Hello nab\\u00edz\\u00edme \\u017e\\u00e1k\\u016fm mo\\u017enost z\\u00edsk\\u00e1n\\u00ed mezin\\u00e1rodn\\u011b uzn\\u00e1van\\u00fdch Cambridge Certificate na \\u00farovn\\u00edch PET, FCE i CEA.</p>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n\\n<div class=\\\"col-md-6\\\"><img class=\\\"img-responsive\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"img\\\\bg-img\\\\bg-2.jpg\\\"><cms-plugin title=\\\"Picture / Image - 4769\\\" alt=\\\"Picture / Image - 4769 \\\" id=\\\"4769\\\"></cms-plugin></div>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n\\n<div class=\\\"carousel-item\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"single-top-popular-course\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"row\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"col-md-6\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"popular-course-content\\\">\\n<h5>CISCO Academy</h5>\\n\\n<p>\\u0160kola je d\\u00edky sv\\u00e9mu vybaven\\u00ed a pro\\u0161kolen\\u00ed lektor\\u016f zapojena do celosv\\u011btov\\u00e9ho vzd\\u011bl\\u00e1vac\