t\\\">\\n<h5>CISCO Academy</h5>\\n\\n<p>\\u0160kola je d\\u00edky sv\\u00e9mu vybaven\\u00ed a pro\\u0161kolen\\u00ed lektor\\u016f zapojena do celosv\\u011btov\\u00e9ho vzd\\u011bl\\u00e1vac\\u00edho programu pro v\\u00fduku s\\u00ed\\u0165ov\\u00fdch specialist\\u016f. Sou\\u010d\\u00e1st\\u00ed p\\u0159\\u00edpravy jsou v\\u00fdukov\\u00e9 materi\\u00e1ly v angli\\u010dtin\\u011b i praktick\\u00e1 cvi\\u010den\\u00ed zam\\u011b\\u0159en\\u00e1 na konfiguraci s\\u00ed\\u0165ov\\u00fdch za\\u0159\\u00edzen\\u00ed. Po \\u00fasp\\u011b\\u0161n\\u00e9m slo\\u017een\\u00ed test\\u016f mohou \\u017e\\u00e1ci z\\u00edskat mezin\\u00e1rodn\\u011b uzn\\u00e1van\\u00e9 certifik\\u00e1ty.</p>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n\\n<div class=\\\"col-md-6\\\"><img class=\\\"img-responsive\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"img\\\\bg-img\\\\bg-2.jpg\\\"><cms-plugin title=\\\"Picture / Image - 1774\\\" id=\\\"1774\\\" alt=\\\"Picture / Image - 1774 \\\"></cms-plugin></div>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n\\n<div class=\\\"carousel-item\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"single-top-popular-course\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"row\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"col-md-6\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"popular-course-content\\\">\\n<h5>P\\u0159edn\\u00e1\\u0161ky a exkurze</h5>\\n\\n<p>P\\u0159edn\\u00e1\\u0161ek na r\\u016fzn\\u00e1 t\\u00e9mata vyslechnou \\u017e\\u00e1ci b\\u011bhem studia mnoho; nejzaj\\u00edmav\\u011bj\\u0161\\u00ed jsou jist\\u011b ty, kdy se maj\\u00ed mo\\u017enost setkat p\\u0159\\u00edmo s odborn\\u00edky z praxe, nez\\u0159\\u00eddka i na\\u0161imi b\\u00fdval\\u00fdmi studenty. Atraktivn\\u00ed jsou i exkurze na univerzitn\\u00ed pracovi\\u0161t\\u011b vybaven\\u00e1 \\u0161pi\\u010dkovou technikou nebo v automatizovan\\u00fdch provozech.</p>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n\\n<div class=\\\"col-md-6\\\"><img class=\\\"img-responsive\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"img\\\\bg-img\\\\bg-2.jpg\\\"><cms-plugin title=\\\"Picture / Image - 1820\\\" id=\\\"1820\\\" alt=\\\"Picture / Image - 1820 \\\"></cms-plugin></div>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n</div