/div>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n\\n<div class=\\\"carousel-item\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"single-top-popular-course\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"row\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"col-md-6\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"popular-course-content\\\">\\n<h5>P\\u0159edn\\u00e1\\u0161ky a exkurze</h5>\\n\\n<p>P\\u0159edn\\u00e1\\u0161ek na r\\u016fzn\\u00e1 t\\u00e9mata vyslechnou \\u017e\\u00e1ci b\\u011bhem studia mnoho; nejzaj\\u00edmav\\u011bj\\u0161\\u00ed jsou jist\\u011b ty, kdy se maj\\u00ed mo\\u017enost setkat p\\u0159\\u00edmo s odborn\\u00edky z praxe, nez\\u0159\\u00eddka i na\\u0161imi b\\u00fdval\\u00fdmi studenty. Atraktivn\\u00ed jsou i exkurze na univerzitn\\u00ed pracovi\\u0161t\\u011b vybaven\\u00e1 \\u0161pi\\u010dkovou technikou nebo v automatizovan\\u00fdch provozech.</p>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n\\n<div class=\\\"col-md-6 p-0\\\"><img class=\\\"img-responsive\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"img\\\\bg-img\\\\bg-2.jpg\\\"><cms-plugin title=\\\"Picture / Image - 6319\\\" alt=\\\"Picture / Image - 6319 \\\" id=\\\"6319\\\"></cms-plugin></div>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n\\n<div class=\\\"carousel-item\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"single-top-popular-course\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"row\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"col-md-6\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"popular-course-content\\\">\\n<h5>Praxe ve firm\\u00e1ch</h5>\\n\\n<p>Na konci t\\u0159et\\u00edho a v pr\\u016fb\\u011bhu cel\\u00e9ho \\u010dtvrt\\u00e9ho ro\\u010dn\\u00edku absolvuj\\u00ed \\u017e\\u00e1ci oboru IT praxi ve firm\\u00e1ch nebo instituc\\u00edch. Deset vybran\\u00fdch student\\u016f vyjelo v roce 2018 na t\\u0159\\u00edt\\u00fddenn\\u00ed st\\u00e1\\u017e do irsk\\u00e9ho Dublinu, aby v r\\u00e1mci odborn\\u00e9 praxe mohli zdokonalit sv\\u00e9 jazykov\\u00e9 znalosti a poznali \\u017eivot v zahrani\\u010d\\u00ed.</p>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n\\n<div class=\\\"col-md-6 p-0\\\"><img class=\\\"img-responsive\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"img\\\\bg-img\\\\bg-2.jpg\\\"><cms-plugin title=\\\"Picture / Image - 6320\\\" alt=\\\"Picture / Image - 6320 \\\" id=\\\"63